    excerpt:
      "Discover how professional designers use layered lighting to enhance ambiance, support function, and transform interior spaces through strategic fixture selection and placement.",
    category: "design-practice",
    author: "IDI Editorial Team",
    publishedAt: "2026-01-26",
    readTime: "13 min read",
    featuredImage: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540932239986-30128078f3c5?w=1200&q=80",
